Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE EXTREME ANNIHILATION SPELL, MEDOROA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get you anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:01:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring some fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The leaders have finished their meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The showdown is in five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So they finally made up their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a collaborative effort\Nbetween countries, so it took a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be gathering in Carl Kingdom,\Nsouth of the Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl Kingdom is in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're using the ruins\Nas a cover to build a base.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Our group will head out the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So for the next four days\NI'm going to my mentor's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, Crocodine and Chiu are all training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys make sure to rest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get ready too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They've all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With the showdown date set,\Nthe Disciples of Aban have all left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Including Dai and Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,His wounds haven't fully healed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he rush into battle so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He only rests when\Nhe's too wounded to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he's cursed to keep fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the only ones\Nwho can save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is support them\Nto ease their burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My weapons can recover\Nfrom this sort of damage on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can fix them if you're in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be\Nin a really bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think the Sword of Champions\Nbeat you because it's made of Orichalcum,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll knock some sense into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Step outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You're going to use a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He knows how to fight with a sword?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'd teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That sword is this world's greatest!\NI can't make anything stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your only hope to fight better\Nis for you to grow stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What hope do you have\Nif you can't match someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is no joke... He's strong!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe someone this good\Nwas still out there in the world.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Those weapons will\Ngo to waste in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they're restored,\NI'll show you how to really use them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,through actual combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Baruji Whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry Chiu.\NI'll need your help with my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely! I'm glad to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, an Orichalcum Superbeing Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not their strength that's bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Their minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Forbidden Magic of giving life\Nto inanimate materials
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is heavily affected by the mentality\Nof whoever uses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Flazzard was created back when Hadorra\Nwas obsessed with power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was a violent piece of trash\Nwho cared only for glory, remember?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If that Royal Guard\Nactually cares about a fair fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,then it means Hadorra himself\Nhas grown as a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the members of the Royal Guard\Ncreated by the new Hadorra
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,are each stronger than Flazzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,until now, you guys have managed\Nto get by using teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're going to use it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentor, please,\Nis there anything I can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym repelled a spell\Nten times stronger than a Merazoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A normal flame spell won't work on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with an Orichalcum body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentor, are you sure you can get up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Flazzard,\Nhe was pretty strong, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He used both fire and ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea was good, but his youth\Nand inexperience caused him to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Had he used fire and ice simultaneously,\Nyou wouldn't have stood a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.\NI've never tried it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do this, and Orichalcum foe or not,\Nyou'll always win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is the Grand Sorcerer\NMatorif's strongest extreme spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What a spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I can manage to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only used it a handful of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mentor's like a walking ball of ego,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and even he's scared to use it?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what kind of spell is it?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire and ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They may seem like opposite spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but both Fire-type and Ice-type spells\Nuse Magic Power that control heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of\Nwhether it's positive or negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Push Magic Power in the positive direction\Nfor a Fire-type spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:09:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Push it in the negative direction\Nfor an Ice-type spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When this positive and negative\NMagic Power is sparked simultaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes\Nthe ultimate annihilating power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, by combining the two powers,\Nit creates an annihilation spell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that will disintegrate anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good. You've grown quite perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Extreme Annihilation Spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Medoroa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Medoroa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This spell is unbelievably hard to cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You need the skill to combine Fire-type\Nand Ice-type spells of exact equal power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But, pull it off and you're unbeatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nhow resilient your opponent is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This spell will disintegrate\Nabsolutely anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're going to teach it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably the only spell\Nthat will work on an Orichalcum enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! How do I do it?!\NWhat sort of training do I need to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, training for this is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll only take an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This spell requires\Ncasting both spells simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be balanced perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those without talent\Nwill never pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cast it at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel it out with your own Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,can only be cancelled out\Nby the same spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't successfully combine\Nthe two spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be erased from this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! That's crazy, Mentor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull it off if you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEHOMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEALING-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}REFRACTOR FIST{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O-Oh crap! This is too much!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to run to dodge it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right! Mentor's not well!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been casting Forbidden Magic-level\Nspells to protect his friends!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's coughed up blood before!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That spell takes such an effort to cast.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he's willing to endure it for me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't run away!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is about more than just a spell!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I run from this,\NI'll have no right to call him my mentor!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Medoroa!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Contain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no! Popp was always better\Nat Fire-type spells!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The output of his left hand\Nis overpowering his right!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Increase your Ice-type spell power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Increase the power from your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't vanish! Don't vanish, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, I wish I could train with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A princess can't just run off\Nand abandon her duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baruji Whirlpool became two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it's one again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Theoretically, it's possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your own training,\Nyet you're helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Punching each drop of water that splashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Training to increase your speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. More speed means more force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I need more instant destructive power\Nto damage our new enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What happened to your arm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing much.\NJust training for a new spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When I mess up, this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just dropped by to cool it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of spell is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find out after I complete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is seriously strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who we face,\NI know I'll be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We have two days left.\NI better try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have to try a lot harder\Nif you want to increase your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're carrying\Na lot of excess weight, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm joking! I'm joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?! Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A trap for grappling training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be facing enemies\Nimmune to my Refractor Fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it. No more gazing at those legs.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those things are lethal.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Balance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about equal balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that, Mentor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know my Fire-type Magic Power\Nis still a bit strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not too far off, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been more impressed\Nwith your skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time\Nyou've ever complimented me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's time you retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids always get ahead of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious, Mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll learn every skill you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to\Npush yourself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to look after yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you choose to be a Mage\Nwhen you became Aban's student?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you consider\Nbeing a Warrior or a Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense a very, very great potential\Nfor magic from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You remind me of an old friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't hesitate to be a Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He really had an eye for people.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me to retire,\Nyou better really impress me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Mystic Legion Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet down in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be executed, but Lord Hadorra\Nmercifully granted you imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't deserve imprisonment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn more remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may, Lord Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Albinass?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That one should be executed at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nothing but a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If allowed to live, he will only\Nbe a hinderance to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the one\Nwho worked to enhance my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It cost him his son.\NThere's no need to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him cool off in his cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, My Lord. If that is your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The old me would have killed him\Nwithout a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I too soft?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You are magnanimous,\Nif a bit too lenient on parasites.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't hold back, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban, I have a job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An assassination?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Hadorra would appreciate\Nme killing the Disciples of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the Disciples.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not even sure you'll succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But at his core, he is still a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,While he remains silent for now,\Nthere's no telling how he'll move next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, eliminate the sleeping Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:07.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:11.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:15.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:19.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:22.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:26.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:30.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:34.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:38.60,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:42.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:47.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:53.58,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:57.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:22:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:22:59.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:03.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:08.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.51,0:23:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.51,0:23:11.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:16.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:22.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and his friends head to Carl Kingdom\Nwhere warriors gather from all over.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the group approaches the stronghold\Nof the Dark Army, the Field of Death,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they renew their resolve\Nto defeat the Dark King.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, on orders from Ban,\NKilban closes in on Baran.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"To the Final Battleground"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:23:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
